{
  "id": "adv_event_2110_01_02",
  "title": "星見市へ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、トリエルのみんな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ It’s the TRINITYAiLE girls!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.3666666666666663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "わ～！　凄いですね～！\nこれ全部手作りですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ this is amazing!\nIs this all handmade?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.566666666666667,
      "endTime": 10.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "ほんま凄いな～\nこんな手のこんだパーティー初めて見たわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s really awesome.\nI have never seen such a well-prepared party before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.4,
      "endTime": 15.866666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "手伝いに来たわ。今朝思い立って\nもうここまで準備しているなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We came to help. You’ve been at it since morning\nand already got so much done…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.066666666666666,
      "endTime": 21.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 21.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "仕事が早めに終わったから\n手伝いに来たわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We got off work early‚\nso we came to help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.6,
      "endTime": 26.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワのみんなも！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All the members of LizNoir too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.4,
      "endTime": 28.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "長瀬麻奈の誕生日パーティー！？　それなら\n大急ぎで打ち合わせを終わらせないと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“A birthday party for Mana Nagase?!\nIn that case‚ we have to finish the meeting quickly!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.566666666666666,
      "endTime": 35.020000081313285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "……って莉央さんが言ってました～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That’s what Rio-san said!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.233333333333334,
      "endTime": 37.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、明日のランニングは何キロ増やしたい？\n五キロ？　それとも十キロ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro‚ how many extra km do you want to run tomorrow?\nFive km? Or ten?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.166666666666664,
      "endTime": 45.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それはご勘弁を～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoah‚ have mercy~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.266666666666666,
      "endTime": 47.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "仲がいいのは素晴らしいけど\n早く手伝いましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s nice to see everyone getting on so well‚\nbut let’s get on with helping.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.3,
      "endTime": 52.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、よろしくね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks‚ we’re glad for your help!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.666666666666664,
      "endTime": 55.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、{user}くーん\nって、あら？　{user}君はどこ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}…\nHuh? Where did {user} get to?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.4,
      "endTime": 62.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.6
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.166666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "さあ？　サボりじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is he skipping out on us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.166666666666664,
      "endTime": 66,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ！　サボってるんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehhh? He’s skipping out?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2,
      "endTime": 68.59999990463257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、適当なことを言わない。愛も信じないで……\nでも……確かにさっきから見ないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro‚ don’t talk like that. And Ai‚ you shouldn’t believe it either.\nBut I haven’t seen him in a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.8,
      "endTime": 77.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　{user}さんから\nメッセージが入ってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ {user}-san sent\nme a text…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 82.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "「用事があるので星見市に行ってくる」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Something came up‚ so I’ve got to go to Hoshimi City.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.16666666666667,
      "endTime": 86.89999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "「パーティーには間に合うように帰るから\n準備、手伝えなくてごめん」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“I’ll be back in time for the party‚\nbut sorry I couldn’t help you get ready.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1,
      "endTime": 93.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……そっか\nそれなら……仕方ないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\nWell‚ it can’t be helped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4,
      "endTime": 97.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "え、え？　どういうことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚eh? What are you talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.66666666666667,
      "endTime": 100.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "たぶん……お姉ちゃんのお墓参りに\n行ってるんだと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think he’s probably going to\nvisit my sister’s grave.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.13333333333334,
      "endTime": 105.16,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "んん？　でも、お墓参りって\n普通は命日にするものですよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? But don’t people usually visit graves\non the person’s death anniversary?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.36666666666666,
      "endTime": 111.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "普通はそう……だよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Normally‚ yes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7,
      "endTime": 114.79999999999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、お姉ちゃんが亡くなった日に行くのは\n凄く辛いと思うから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I think it’d be really tough to visit\non the day she died‚ so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115,
      "endTime": 121.1733333874774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "だから、暗くならないように\n誕生日に行ったのかもしれないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So maybe he went on her birthday\nto avoid it being so gloomy.",
        "id": ""
      },
